Combining method

I am going to start with the PCs that capture 90% of the original variance in the dataset (i.e.PC1 to PC7)

wisc.pr.hclust <- hclust(dist(wisc.pr$x[,1:7]), method = "ward.D2")
plot(wisc.pr.hclust)

grps <- cutree(wisc.pr.hclust,k=2)
